bmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2Fbe4db414ad005ee7c504588cbedb6e48&h=9859dae8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/AchingOblongCornsnake-size_restricted.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FAchingOblongCornsnake-size_restricted.gif&h=b8311179&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ZSwasP2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FZSwasP2.gif&h=dbe52e17&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/7/70/The_Equalizer_2_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F7%2F70%2FThe_Equalizer_2_Poster.jpg&h=caf82e2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.憤世嫉俗的年輕商人克勞迪歐趕著要和客戶進行重要會議，卻受困在羅馬辦公室的電梯中，隨即演變成一場不可收拾的夢魘。在電梯之外，某種致命病毒正在大肆擴散，受到傳染者將變成極端狂暴的活死人。克勞迪歐必須千方百計想逃出電梯，然而，這部與世隔絕的電梯似乎已變成全市最安全的地方&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n2.故事敘述當香港最高的摩天大樓遭到恐怖襲擊時，現擔任保全的前FBI組長威爾&middot;索耶，並被指為罪魁禍首；為一洗清白，必須冒著生命危險進入大樓中，以解救受困的民眾和家人，同時他也必須找出幕後真兇。 <br />\n<br />\n3.故事敘述勞勃&middot;麥考在行俠仗義的過程中，得知自己的老友蘇珊遭人謀殺；這使麥考決定走回老路，找出並制裁盯上自己的人<br />\n<br />\n7 00PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> *第3套係薯片版<br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=RDHuQFEb0OcDjtLBD%2BwlzROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=13712569\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=RDHuQFEb0OcDjtLBD%2BwlzROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=a5485fd4\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"575bc70ae0bbc0c42fdd166e40af2a8117f68792","tid":808463,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T10:47:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68b41ae4cce93cbb0f79c8b5d49c9054a83d317f","tid":808463,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T11:01:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af89e5398667038cff0583a1f8c71eb61b498d10","tid":808463,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T12:21:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}